author: dblevins
msg: Fixed the namespace used for referencing the wsdl

author: gdamour
msg: o aggregate functions are now partially supported. At least they do not
o EJBQL returned types are extracted. This allows:
* in the case of finders, to check that the returned type is the abstract
schema type of the owning EJB.
* in the case of selects, to return the relevant type.
o EJBQL queries use EJB abstract schema names instead of EJB names.

author: gdamour
msg: It is no more required to add found entities to the InTxCache. TranQL
adds them itself if they are not already in the InTxCache.

author: adc
msg: Removal of old automapping code in preparation for mapping service.
